Package model

Class Appointment

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Appointment
  • public class Appointment
extends java.lang.Object
    Model class for an Appointment from the database. Contains data members corresponding to the data from the database. Class methods include getters and setters for data members.

    See Also:
    AppointmentsManager
